messages.message: Can I give someone a gift card to fix the processfiles additional options to be check boxes or something a customer can use?

Something that I chatted with @cross talk - a podcast about crosswords - listen on apple podcasts or spotify about, but maybe the Frontend team can take on your request and see how they want to handle it! — fyi @Jessica @Eric Han

I’ll make a ticket tomorrow and try to outline some of the options. I looked into this a couple of months ago but found that any route we take will involve a lot more changes than one would think, so just ended up making it show at least what the different options are.
